[Time will tell how predictive the Canadian surveillance is but increasing
the frequency of inspection visits cannot do any harm and certainly much
good. I suspect that the actions based on this negative test were more
political than scientific. But subject to the alternative of an indefinite
or long extended farm quarantine there was probably little choice of action
and the vital need to keep the elk farmers' support. - Mod.MHJ
